content: That's really interesting, thanks for explaining the genetic differences between Indian and Irish populations. Speaking of my Indian side, I was talking to my mom last week and she reminded me that our Indian side is actually a mix of Gujarati and Punjabi, which explains my love for spicy food and good old-fashioned Bollywood music. Do you know if there are any specific genetic differences between Gujarati and Punjabi populations that might affect my health?
